txt.en: Commander Mozgúth can be found at Zudramdân.\n\nYou should find and defeat Commander Mozgúth.
You have successfully defeated Commander Mozgúth.

'I have urgent need of someone with your skill set, [placeholder]. There is a vile Orkish leader, Commander Mozgúth. He has taken control of the ruins of Zudramdân! Yes, you have heard me correctly! We had only recently secured those ruins for ourselves. When the war began, we could not hold Zudramdân and had to fall back. I ask of you, infiltrate Zudramdân, find their commander, and defeat the Orc wretch. Can I count on you?'
You have successfully defeated Commander Mozgúth. Those with the war effort will be pleased with what you have accomplished today.
When conflict broke out, Zudramdân was the first hold to be lost to the Orkish forces of Gundabad.
